data.description: This is your opportunity to own a piece of paradise in our amazing Florida State. Don't miss a 4 bedroom and 3 bath one story house sit in a BIG LOT of more than $17,000 square feet with an oversized pool and 2 tikis for your leisure. One of the Bedrooms is converted in a 1 bed and 1 bath apartment to help with mortgage, can be easily be removed just opening the door to access the house. Large Spacious areas, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, wood cabinets. Big backyard with fruit trees and more.... This house has NO association in a very desirable area. Close to expressways, A+ schools, malls, restaurants , etc...REDUCED FOR A QUICK SALE! Must see to appreciate!
